sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy / oauth-proxy)
    participant VLLM_HTTP as vllm-rocm Container<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant VLLM_GRPC as vllm-rocm Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant GPU as AMD ROCm GPU<br/>PCIe/HIP
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(S3/PVC) 443/TCP

    Note over VLLM_HTTP,S3: Flow 3: Model Loading (Startup)
    VLLM_HTTP->>S3: Load model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 or filesystem<br/>Auth: IAM/SA credentials
    S3-->>VLLM_HTTP: Model artifacts & tokenizer
    VLLM_HTTP->>GPU: Transfer weights to VRAM<br/>PCIe/Device API

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>AuthProxy: Forward request<br/>TLS terminated at gateway
    AuthProxy->>VLLM_HTTP: HTTP/8000<br/>Auth enforced at proxy
    VLLM_HTTP->>GPU: Tensor operations<br/>PCIe/HIP Runtime
    GPU-->>VLLM_HTTP: Inference result
    VLLM_HTTP-->>AuthProxy: JSON response
    AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: gRPC/TGIS Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerateStream<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>AuthProxy: Forward request<br/>TLS terminated at gateway
    AuthProxy->>VLLM_GRPC: gRPC/8033<br/>Auth enforced at proxy
    VLLM_GRPC->>GPU: Tensor operations<br/>PCIe/HIP Runtime
    GPU-->>VLLM_GRPC: Inference result
    VLLM_GRPC-->>AuthProxy: gRPC response stream
    AuthProxy-->>Gateway: Forward response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response stream
